  "title" : "Is it possible to access user session using ProxyContext, the same was as we can using RoutingContext?",
  "body" : "<p>In <strong>Eclipse Vert.x</strong>, while using Vert.x Web, applying <strong>session handler</strong> to the router, allows us to access the session using <strong>RoutingContext</strong>, in the handler. Is there any way we can access the session using <strong>ProxyContext</strong>, which is used in <strong>ProxyInterceptor</strong> implementation?</p>\n"
